      </a>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <!-- ===== CTA ===== -->
  <section class="article-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="article-cta__body">
        <h2>Ready to design your Japan revenue system?</h2>
        <p>Tell us where you are: what you have tried, where you are seeing friction, and what you are trying to solve. We will be direct about whether and how we can help.</p>
        <div class="article-cta__actions">
          <a href="/en/contact/" class="article-cta__btn article-cta__btn--primary">Talk to us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

